    <briefdescription>
<para>STM32 CAN wrapper — wraps bxCAN (CAN_HandleTypeDef) or FDCAN (FDCAN_HandleTypeDef) for <ref refid="classBaseCan" kindref="compound">BaseCan</ref> interface. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Users configure CAN/FDCAN in STM32CubeMX, then pass the handle here. Basic CAN 2.0 is supported out of the box; FDCAN flags are available but data-phase bitrate configuration requires the FDCAN HAL extensions.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="author"><para>HardFOC </para>
